                                                <i class="text-muted small">34 Comments</i>
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <a href="#">
                                                <span class="post-img">
                                                    <img src="~/assets/images/blog/post-3.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                                                </span>
                                                <h4 class="text-uppercase text-primary">LOGO</h4>
                                                <i class="text-muted small">34 Comments</i>
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <a href="#">
                                                <span class="post-img">
                                                    <img src="~/assets/images/blog/post-4.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive" />
                                                </span>
                                                <h4 class="text-uppercase text-primary">MARKETING #2</h4>
                                                <i class="text-muted small">34 Comments</i>
